scripts.localbuild: npm run commit && ng build --configuration=production && npm run deploy
scripts.commit: git add -A && git commit -m 'an other commit' && git push
scripts.deploy: aws s3 rm s3://$npm_package_config_host --recursive && aws s3 sync ./dist/yet s3://$npm_package_config_host  --cache-control='max-age=31536000' && aws cloudfront create-invalidation --distribution-id E10G6CFC9CLUBD --paths '/*'
scripts.sendConfig: aws s3 rm s3://spec.yet.expert --recursive && aws s3 sync ./specs s3://spec.yet.expert && aws cloudfront create-invalidation --distribution-id $npm_package_config_speccloudfront --paths '/*'
